zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ams1665703130099.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ams1665703130099.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ams1665703130099.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ams1665703130099\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">trigger close \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ams1665703130099__trigger_close_393020\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Interactive trigger that handles processing to close a tree node so that its subordinate tree items are no longer shown in the list view of a Tree widget.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ams1665703130099__topic_d116816e1_d116817e1_d116818e1\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104ams1665703130099_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"ams1665703130099__codeblock_ayf_1mg_fcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger close\nparams\n   string control : in ; TREE | LIST | KEYBOARD\n   string item : in\nendparams\n\n; &lt;Your code here&gt;\n\nend ; trigger close</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"ams1665703130099__section_w418ab1b7b5_w419ab1b7_w420ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ams1665703130099__table_d14384e1_d14385e1_d14386e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Applies to:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Form widgets: <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gge1665702634237.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gge1665702634237.html\" title=\"The utree widget enables users to view and navigate structured data as a hierarchy. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tree, which is mapped to utree.\">utree (Tree)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Activation:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Activated when the user clicks an expanded tree node so that its subordinate tree items will no longer be shown in the list view.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Default behavior:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n None\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Behavior upon completion:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n None\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ams1665703130099__topic_d82967e1_d82968e1_d82969e1_d82970e1_d82971e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d225698e128\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ams1665703130099__li_d44426e1_d44427e1_d44428e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword parmname\">control</span>—input control used by the user; one of:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ams1665703130099__li_d44429e1_d44430e1_d44431e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">TREE</code>—user clicked in the tree view\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ams1665703130099__li_d44432e1_d44433e1_d44434e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">LIST</code>—user clicked in the list view\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ams1665703130099__li_d44435e1_d44436e1_d44437e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">KEYBOARD</code>—user performed a keyboard action\n </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ams1665703130099__li_d44438e1_d44439e1_d44440e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword parmname\">item</span>—value of the selected tree node\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525777\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525777\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "trigger close Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 trigger close Interactive trigger that handles processing to close a tree node so that its subordinate tree items are no longer shown in the list view of a Tree widget. Explain this code trigger close params string control : in ; TREE | LIST | KEYBOARD string item : in endparams ; <Your code here> end ; trigger close Copy Applies to: Form widgets: utree (Tree) Activation: Activated when the user clicks an expanded tree node so that its subordinate tree items will no longer be shown in the list view. Default behavior: None Behavior upon completion: None Parameters control —input control used by the user; one of: TREE —user clicked in the tree view LIST —user clicked in the list view KEYBOARD —user performed a keyboard action item —value of the selected tree node Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}